'From Squeak 2.0 of May 22, 1998 on 17 June 1998 at 9:34:24 am'!"Change Set:		copyRefCleanupDate:			17 June 1998Author:			Scott WallaceFixes a small oversight in the copyRefMethods-sw update of 6/16/98"!!Player class methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'sw 6/16/1998 15:32'!copyStateFrom: anotherClass	| dupScript |	scripts _ IdentityDictionary new.	anotherClass userScriptsDo:		[:aScript | 			aScript isAnonymous ifFalse:				[dupScript _ aScript shallowCopy.				dupScript initializeForPlayer: self flagshipInstance afterShallowCopyFrom: aScript.				scripts at: aScript selector put: dupScript]].	slotInfo _ anotherClass slotInfo deepCopy.	self copyAddedStateFrom: anotherClass.  "The player-ref jump table"! !